sequenceDiagram
    participant Platform as Platform Operator<br/>(rhods-operator)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant AIGW as ai-gateway-operator<br/>Controller Manager
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant BatchOp as batch-gateway-operator
    participant BatchAPI as Batch API Server
    participant BatchProc as Batch Processor
    participant BatchGC as Garbage Collector

    Note over Platform,K8sAPI: Flow 1: AIGateway Reconciliation

    Platform->>K8sAPI: Create AIGateway CR<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>AIGW: Watch event: AIGateway created<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA Token

    AIGW->>AIGW: Read spec.batchGateway.managementState
    AIGW->>Kustomize: Select manifests based on spec<br/>(in-process rendering)
    Kustomize-->>AIGW: Rendered manifests

    AIGW->>K8sAPI: Apply rendered manifests<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    Note over AIGW,K8sAPI: Status reporting pipeline
    AIGW->>K8sAPI: Update AIGateway status<br/>(version, platform, conditions)

    Note over AIGW,BatchGC: Flow 2: Batch Gateway Deployment (when managementState=Managed)

    AIGW->>K8sAPI: Deploy batch-gateway CRD<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    AIGW->>K8sAPI: Deploy batch-gateway RBAC<br/>(ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding, SA)
    AIGW->>K8sAPI: Deploy batch-gateway Deployment<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    K8sAPI-->>BatchOp: Pod starts, begins watching<br/>LLMBatchGateway CRs

    Note over BatchOp,BatchGC: Flow 3: LLMBatchGateway Workload Deployment

    BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Watch LLMBatchGateway CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>BatchOp: LLMBatchGateway created

    BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create API Server Deployment<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>BatchAPI: Pod starts

    BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create Processor Deployment<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>BatchProc: Pod starts

    BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create GC Deployment<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>BatchGC: Pod starts

    BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create cert-manager Certificate<br/>for TLS
    BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute<br/>for Gateway API ingress
    BatchOp->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor,<br/>PodMonitor, PrometheusRule
